** MSG
E-01 FACTORY CODE IS WRONG
E-02 DATE IS NOT RIGHT.
E-03 INPUT MACHINE NO
E-04 FACILITY MANAGEMENT M/F DOES NOT INCLUDE IT
E-05 FACILITY MANAGEMENT M/F HAS CANCELLED ALREADY.
E-06 THIS DATA HAS INPUT ALREADY.
E-07 MORE THAN 720 MINUTES STOPPING TIME IS NOT RIGHT.
E-08 TOTAL STOP TIME IS MORE THAN 720 MIN. THAT ISN'T RIGHT
E-09 INPUT ACTUAL NUMBER.
E-10 NIGHT AND DAY INSTRUCTION IS <H, Y>.
E-11 INPUT OPERATION TIME.
E-12 OPERATION TIME IS MORE THAN 12H THAT IS NOT RIGHT.
E-13 ACTUAL NUMBER IS TOO BIG.
E-14 INPUT UNINHABITED PRODUCTION NUMBER OF BOXES
E-15 INPUT UNINHABITED PRODUCTION NUMBER.
E-16 UNINHABITED PRODUCTION NUMBER IS TOO BIG.
E-17 STOPPED TIME IS BIGGER THAN OPERATION TIME
